@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_htotup(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.36
    v2 = ((0.68 - (v2 + 0.77 + v1 + 0.14)) + ((tmp + 0.02 - v2 + 0.06) - 0.63))
    tmp = 0.30
    tmp = ((v2 + v0) * 0.40)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.30 + v2 + 0.60)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v1 + 0.25 * v0 + 0.72)))
    data[tid] = v0
